		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=173#comment-105">
			October 16, 2012 at 8:38 am</a>		</div>

		<p>Ummm&#8230; I have a problem.3:30 pm is 21:30 pm in Israel, and I can&#8217;t be here at this hour. Just on Friday. What to do?</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/?p=173&#038;replytocom=105#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-105", "105", "respond", "173")'>Reply</a>		</div>
