		<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/5ee84c3aa3cca5fb838a31fd5fef0073?s=32&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.us.ekoloko.com%2Fwp-includes%2Fimages%2Fblank.gif&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />		<cite class="fn">admin</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>

		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=173#comment-106">
			October 16, 2012 at 9:47 am</a>		</div>

		<p>The ceremony this week at 3:30 is for the Advanced Rangers who were Rangers of the Week the last 2 weeks. New Rangers of the Week from THIS week will have their ranger ceremony NEXT week. We will try to hold it next Wednesday instead of Thursday.</p>

		<div class="reply">
